  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 8b94c1195cc9272d99a82df3df77782b, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  ArtifactForm: 1
  Names:
  - The Tutorialus
  Lines:
  - Phew! You must have thought long and hard before letting me in.
  - And you know I'm your teacher, Tutorialus Invisiblehonius!
  - Ahem. Anyway.
  - Take the forms, those green books on the top right. Not now! Let me finish!
  - Read the forms carefully and select Transfer to resolve my complaint as a Magical
    Artifact.
  - You know... It's hard to remember a magical artifact you can't see...
  - After that, a whole bunch of disgruntled artifacts will be waiting for you outside
    the door.
  - Be on your guard! It's quite difficult to figure out what their requests are,
    but I think you'll get it after a couple of tries!
  - They won't fire you on your first day, will they? Haha!
  - 'And so. Briefly again. '
  - Open the door, listen to the complaint, fill out the form, and so on, get it?
  - "Remember \u2014 my form is Transfer!"
  - Well. I'm off. Good luck!
